hooks.prompt:
You must respond with ONLY a JSON object, no other text.

Input: $ARGUMENTS

First: Check if "stop_hook_active" is true in the input. If yes, respond exactly: {"ok":true}

Otherwise: Did this session involve WezTerm configuration or terminal customization work?

If YES, respond exactly: {"ok":false,"reason":"Ask user about WezTerm learnings to save to the plugin's learnings.md"}

If NO, respond exactly: {"ok":true}
